    <string name="privacy_policy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_content">This privacy policy has been prepared to inform you about the information collected, used, and shared during the use of services provided by NeoCard.\n\n1. Information Collected\n\n- User Information: Name, surname, email address.\n- Business Card Data: Business cards created by users, added connections, and shares.\n- Job Postings and Posts: Content created by users in the application.\n- Subscription Information: Premium membership status, payment information, and subscription period.\n- Promotion Code Usage: Promotion codes used and usage dates.\n- Device and Usage Information: Technical data such as IP address, browser information, device model, and operating system.\n\n2. Use of Information\n\nCollected information may be used for the following purposes:\n- Account creation and authentication processes\n- Business card sharing and connection management\n- Job posting and content sharing services\n- Premium subscription management and billing processes\n- Verification and monitoring of promotion code usage\n- Improving application performance and ensuring security\n- Showing users personalized content and advertisements\n- Managing in-app purchases\n\n3. Sharing of Information\n\n- Payment Service Providers: Payment information necessary to complete subscription processes.\n- Certain information may be shared with authorized authorities as required by legal obligations.\n- Personal information is not shared with third parties without users\' explicit consent.\n\n4. Security\n\n- Industry standard technical and administrative measures are taken for the security of user information.\n- Payment information is protected using encryption technologies.\n- However, no data transmission over the internet is 100% secure.\n\n5. Subscriptions and Payments\n\n- Premium subscriptions are managed through Google Play.\n- Subscription fees, renewal terms, and cancellation processes are subject to Google Play Store rules.\n- Memberships earned through promotion codes are valid for a specific period and automatically end at the end of the period.\n\n6. Changes\n\n- This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Users will be informed about important changes via email or application notifications.\n\n7. Contact\n\n- For questions about the privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at info@neocardapp.com.</string>
    
    <string name="about_app_title">About the App</string>
    <string name="about_app_content">NeoCard is an innovative platform that allows users to create digital business cards, share them, and add other users\' business cards to their connections. You can also expand your professional network by sharing job postings and posts.\n\n- Key Features\n\n- Create personal or corporate business cards by registering and logging in\n\n- Share your business cards and add others\' business cards to your connections\n\n- Share job postings and posts\n\n- In-app ads and premium membership options\n\n- Modern interface for secure and fast use\n\nNeoCard is designed to help you build stronger connections in the professional world. Start now and expand your network!</string>
    
    <string name="help_support_title">Help and Support</string>
    <string name="help_support_content">For your questions or technical issues, you can check the following topics:\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQ)\n\n1. I can\'t create an account, what should I do?\nFirst, check your internet connection. If the problem persists, make sure the email address you used during registration is correct.\n\n2. How to create a business card?\nThere is a \'+\' for the \'Create Business Card\' section in the bottom menu options, you can create your business card by entering the required information.\n\n3. How to share a job posting or post?\nYou can create your job posting or post by clicking the \'Share Posting\' button on the profile page.\n\n4. How to purchase a premium membership?\nYou can complete the payment process by clicking the \'Premium Membership\' button on the profile page.\n\n5. How can I use a promotion code?\nIf there is an active promotion code on the profile page, the \'Use Promotion Code\' card appears, and you can enter your code by clicking on it. When you enter a valid code, you will earn a 1-week premium membership.\n\n6. How do I delete my account?\nYou can complete the process by going to the \'Delete My Account\' option from the Settings menu. Caution: This action cannot be undone!\n\nContact the Support Team\n\nFor your questions, you can contact us at info@neocardapp.com. Our support team will assist you as soon as possible.</string>
    
